name: Super Beanstalk Bounce!
description:
How high can you make the beanstalk grow?

Jump on the leaves to find out!

Use arrow keys to move and up arrow to jump (the longer you hold it, the higher you jump)

Made in a weekend for the 20 second game jam:

https://itch.io/jam/20-second-game-jam

Made using Godot by modifying the platformer template
